### NPM ###

npm install --save react react-dom flux

npm install --save webpack

npm install --save babel-core
npm install --save babel-loader
npm install --save babel-preset-react

devtool: 'source-map'?

Webpack --w


COMMANDS:

1. npm init --yes
2. decide/add dependencies to pacakge.json
3. npm install   ==> creates node_modules folder from dependencies
4. Set up config for webpack.config.js
5. Create the frontend folder
6. webpack --w
7. Place bundle.js and node_modules in .gitignore




### Git Hub ###
Clone repository:
1. Copy HTTPS from github site
2. On terminal: git clone url
